    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Verbascum cylleneum are inflammation, fever, coughs, diarrhea, bronchitis, and asthma, which are effectively managed due to the plant's anti-inflammatory and antiseptic properties. Verbascum cylleneum's expectorant properties also help alleviate respiratory issues such as bronchitis and coughs. Additionally, the plant's antispasmodic properties aid in soothing digestive issues and eczema, while its antiallergic properties help alleviate skin irritation and allergies. Furthermore, Verbascum cylleneum's antiseptic and antimicrobial properties facilitate wound healing, reduce the risk of infection, and alleviate sore throats, insect bites, and cold sores. By also exhibiting antifungal properties, the plant is effective in treating fungal infections and pneumonia.",
