    "preparations_description": "The main herbal preparations of Verbascum cylleneum are infusion, tincture, tea, salve, and ointment. Infusion is a liquid extract prepared from dried flowers, used to treat respiratory issues like bronchitis and coughs. The flowers are also used to make a tincture, a concentrated liquid extract used to treat various health conditions. The leaves and stems of Verbascum cylleneum are used to prepare a salve, a topical application used for wound healing and skin conditions, while the flowers are used to make an ointment, a topical application used for skin conditions like eczema. Tea made from the flowers of Verbascum cylleneum is used to treat respiratory issues like bronchitis, coughs, and sore throats.",
